{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_016RSTFtND6giXT9MHz3aXMJ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01Fuh5RSe6iN1WJHgCxERGap","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"git add scripts/set-version.sh scripts/tests/test_set_version.sh scripts/agent-test.sh scripts/hooks/pre-push && git commit -m \"$(cat <<'EOF'\nfeat(11c-2): set-version.sh + pre-push hook + tests\n\nRestore scripts/set-version.sh as the two-axis single-source-of-truth\nfor version writes and consistency checks. Three modes:\n\n  --workspace <new>     Updates Cargo [workspace.package].version,\n                        src/python/pyproject.toml [project].version,\n                        and src/ts/package.json top-level \"version\".\n                        Does NOT touch Axis E.\n  --embedder-api <new>  Updates only\n                        src/rust/crates/fathomdb-embedder-api/Cargo.toml.\n  --check-files         Verifies Axis W lockstep across the three\n                        Axis-W manifests, asserts every workspace\n                        crate (except fathomdb-embedder-api) inherits\n                        the workspace version, and asserts\n                        fathomdb-embedder-api carries an explicit\n                        Axis E [package].version.\n\nAll writes are atomic (mktemp + mv). Idempotent re-runs touch\nnothing the second time. Unknown flags and missing args exit 2 with\nusage on stderr.\n\nscripts/hooks/pre-push runs `set-version.sh --check-files` before\nagent-verify so version drift surfaces with an actionable error\ninstead of being inferred from a downstream typecheck failure.\nResolves the deferred note in dev/plans/ci-deferred.md\n§ scripts/set-version.sh — Phase 11.\n\nscripts/tests/test_set_version.sh covers all three modes, an Axis W\ndrift, an Axis E inheritance regression, idempotence, and the two\nusage-error paths. Wired into scripts/agent-test.sh so\nagent-verify exercises it.\nEOF\n)\"","description":"Commit set-version.sh + hook + tests"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":283,"cache_read_input_tokens":73548,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":283},"output_tokens":68,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"4cda15f5-dd21-46d9-b4db-04d61e252748","uuid":"31ab4df6-dfbf-41a5-9bd0-6f96aaeb340a"}
